4 Paris Olympics had said in a statement that there was \\\"never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group,\\\" and that they had tried to \\\"celebrate community tolerance.\\\"\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1651, \"end\": 1659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a spokesperson\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1703}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1727}, {\"ngram\": \"an intention\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1762}, {\"ngram\": \"any religious group\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1804}, {\"ngram\": \"community tolerance\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Clearly there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group,\\\" Descamps said in the statement.\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1950, \"end\": 1958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an intention\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1905}, {\"ngram\": \"any religious group\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1947}, {\"ngram\": \"the statement\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On the contrary, I think [with] Thomas Jolly, we really did try to celebrate community tolerance.\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 2080, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the contrary\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 1998}, {\"ngram\": \"community tolerance\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2079}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Looking at the result of the polls that we shared, we believe that this ambition was achieved.\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2175, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2102}, {\"ngram\": \"the polls\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"this ambition\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If people have taken offense we are, of course, really, really sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2185}, {\"ngram\": \"offense\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2204}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Barron continued to criticize the apology, \\\"I love this, 'We tried to celebrate community tolerance.'\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2248, \"end\": 2254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999956100964, \"rank\": 4.388505894091456e-09, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the apology\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2289}, {\"ngram\": \"community tolerance\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yeah, tolerance.\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2366, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Except, for those pesky 2.6 billion Christians on the planet, everyone's welcome, everyone's tolerated.\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2470, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2403, \"end\": 2413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.5790939635615081, \"rank\": 0.7240176681261816, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the planet\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All this lovely diversity, until you get to anyone that disagrees with your ideology, like these 2.6 billion people.\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2587, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All this lovely diversity\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2496}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"your ideology\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2555}, {\"ngram\": \"these 2.6 billion people\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2586}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, do not give me this business about tolerance and diversity.\\\"\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2652, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this business\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2620}, {\"ngram\": \"tolerance\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2636}, {\"ngram\": \"diversity\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And then, 'We believe this ambition celebrating tolerance was achieved,'\\\" Barron added.\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2729, \"end\": 2735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999956100964, \"rank\": 4.388505894091456e-09, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this ambition\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2690}, {\"ngram\": \"tolerance\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2712}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Well, I wonder what planet they are living on if they think harmony and peace and all this was achieved by this clear affront to Christians.\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2873, \"end\": 2883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.5790939635615081, \"rank\": 0.7240176681261816, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what planet\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2770}, {\"ngram\": \"harmony\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2811}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2821}, {\"ngram\": \"this clear affront\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2869}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And, then at the very end, a standard bit of condescension, 'If people have taken any offense, we are truly sorry.'\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 3000, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the very end\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 2910}, {\"ngram\": \"condescension\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 2943}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 2955}, {\"ngram\": \"any offense\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 2978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In other words, if you are so simple-minded and stupid to have been offended by this wonderful expression of French culture, well, you know, we are sorry about that.\\\"\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3110, \"end\": 3124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French culture\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other words\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3015}, {\"ngram\": \"this wonderful expression\", \"from\": 3081, \"to\": 3106}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bishop added that Christians were offended by the display \\\"because it was offensive.\\\"\", \"from\": 3169, \"to\": 3258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3191, \"end\": 3201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.5790939635615081, \"rank\": 0.7240176681261816, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The bishop\", \"from\": 3169, \